flowRoot.flowPara: Warning: don't expect to receive mobile signal in the Peak District!
Walking groups are free to stay at The Ramblers Inn for food and drinks. Trains run from Edale to Manchester at the following times.
Note that Edale train station has two separate entrances: ensure that you use the right one for your return journey.
All the guided walks will begin and end at The Rambler Inn, which is located close to the train station. Food is available for those who want to eat.
